<troubleshooting>
- **"File not found in INDEX"**: Stop. Ask user for the path.
- **"Context too large"**: Stop reading. Use `@` to focus on a single file.
- **"Looping errors"**: Pause. Analyze the traceback. Do not blindly retry the same code.
</troubleshooting>
